  "last_query": {
    "query": "How do I add a YouTube video?",
    "answer": "To add a YouTube video to your OptiSigns display, follow these steps:\n\n*   Log in to your [OptiSigns portal](http://app.optisigns.com/).\n*   Navigate to **Files/Assets**, click **App**, and select **YouTube** (or **YouTube Live**).\n*   Enter a **Name** for the asset and paste the full **URL** of the YouTube video.\n    *   *Note: For YouTube Shorts, you must change `/shorts/` in the URL to `/embed/` for it to display correctly.*\n*   Click **Save** to finish creating the asset.\n*   You can then assign the video to your screen, playlist, or schedule.\n\nArticle URL: https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/360051014713-How-to-use-YouTube-with-OptiSigns",
